ing post-apocalyptic land into working rocketry.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371750/extras/3._Start_from_Nothing.gif?t=1683806843\" /><br><br>So, you start by digging Wells which produce and propagate Water.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371750/extras/4._Water.gif?t=1683806843\" /><br><br>Then you create Tilled Earth, which receives that Water and becomes Farmland, which in turn produces Food.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371750/extras/5._Till.gif?t=1683806843\" /><br><br>You can build up your infrastructure to support solar farms and hydroponics labs to stock sleek generational ships that each rescue thousands of evacuees.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371750/extras/6._Infrastructure.gif?t=1683806843\" /><br><br>Or, you can remain low-tech and brute force your population off the Earth by building massive numbers of 1960s era rocketry.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371750/extras/7._Low_Tech.gif?t=1683806843\" /><br><br>And, that's T-Minus 30. A timeboxed city builder that focuses on resource propagation, exploration, and saving as much of humanity as you can before the Earth explodes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371750/extras/8._Rockets.gif?t=1683806843\" /><br><br>Mind you, however you play, you can't save everyone, and people will still end up dead.<br><br>But that's life.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore abandoned ruins of a once-bustling civilization.<br></li><li> Mine skyscrapers and junkyards to reclaim plastics and metals.<br></li><li> Explore procedurally generated landscapes, from small, arid maps with scarce resources to large, forested maps replete with ancient ruins.<br></li><li> Create the infrastructure to convey energy, water, and other resources to your ever-expanding base of operations.<br></li><li> Save as many souls as you can before the world ends in 30 minutes!</li></ul>","developers":["Dejobaan Games","Grey Alien Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371750/header.jpg?t=1683806843","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256848616,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256848616/movie480.mp4?t=1683806832","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256848616/movie_max.mp4?t=1683806832"},"name":"Launch Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256848616/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1683806832","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256848616/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1683806832","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256848616/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1683806832"}},{"highlight":true,"id":256849312,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256849312/movie480.mp4?t=1683806836","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256849312/movie_max.mp4?t=1683806836"},"name":"Dev Gameplay","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256849312/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1683806836","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256849312/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1683806836","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256849312/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1683806836"}}],"name":"T-Minus 30","package_groups":[{"description":"","display_type":0,"is_recurring_subscription":"false","name":"default","save_text":"","selection_text":"Select a purchase option","subs":[{"can_get_free_license":"0","is